headline: HPE Now Powers New AI-Ready Supercomputer Set to Transform Environmental Forecasting in New Zealand
summary: AUCKLAND, New Zealand, September 21, 2025--HPE (NYSE:HPE) today announced that Earth Sciences New Zealand (formally NIWA) of Aotearoa (New Zealand) selected HPE Cray XD2000, purpose-built for AI and simulation workloads, to accelerate the organization’s environmental science and precision of meteorological forecasting.
